#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 12. Paṭhamasūriyūpamasutta → suriyasuttaṃ (bj) | suriyassa upamā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Paṭhamasūriyūpamasutta "
msgstr "12. The Simile of the Sun (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.12:1.1"
msgid "“Sūriyassa, bhikkhave, udayato etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—aruṇuggaṃ; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the dawn is the forerunner and precursor of the sunrise. "

#. VAR: etaṃ nimittaṃ → pubbanimittaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.12:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ uppādāya etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ nimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā. "
msgstr "In the same way, for a mendicant good friendship is the forerunner and precursor of the arising of the seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.12:1.3"
msgid "Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—satta bojjhaṅge bhāvessati, satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkarissati. "
msgstr "A mendicant with good friends can expect to develop and cultivate the seven awakening factors. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.79, sc2
msgctxt "sn46.12:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the seven awakening factors? "

msgctxt "sn46.12:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn46.12:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti, satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the seven awakening factors.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.12:2.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

